Restaurant Sales Forecasting System
Implementation Process Breakdown
Phase 1: Define the Business Goal
Objective

Build a forecasting system that predicts 7-day net sales by store using historical sales data.

Primary goal

Give managers a reliable starting point for:

labor scheduling
prep planning
inventory ordering
daily operational planning
Initial scope

Start with only:

date
store_id
net_sales

Do not start with labor, weather, guest counts, or inventory yet. Keep phase one simple and focused.

