Phase 11: IT and Security Controls
Recommended controls
Control	Purpose
Dedicated VM/workstation	isolates forecasting workload
Least privilege access	limits data exposure
Read-only source access	protects POS/reporting data
Write-only report output	controls report generation
Virtual environment	isolates Python packages
No POS write-back	reduces operational risk
Logging	tracks script runs and failures
Security model
Sales Export Folder → Forecast VM → Output Report Folder

The script should not directly modify POS or operational systems.

Phase 12: Automation

Once the pilot works, automate the workflow.

Daily process
