Phase 15: Optional Machine Learning Model

Only move to PyTorch or ML after the baseline model proves value.

Use ML when
you have enough clean history
multiple stores are involved
event/holiday/weather variables are available
baseline forecasts are useful but limited
you want automatic pattern learning
Do not use ML just because it sounds advanced.

The baseline model is easier to explain and easier to approve.

