Executive Summary Version

The implementation should begin with a controlled pilot using existing sales export data. The first version should forecast daily net sales by store using a simple trimmed-average model. The system should run in a dedicated, secure Python environment with read-only access to source data and report-only output. After a 2–4 week pilot, the organization can evaluate forecast accuracy, manager usefulness, and whether to expand into guest counts, labor forecasting, inventory planning, or machine learning enhancements.
